<h1>What requires IRB?</h1>
<ul>
<li><p>Why not journalism? What makes research different?</p>
<ul>
<li><p>Systematic scientific valid research</p></li>
<li><p>Generalizable data/results, etc.</p></li>
<li><p>(Systematic interviewing) - YOU ARE THE INSTRUMENT</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
</section><section class="slide level2">
<h1>Next steps...</h1>
<ul>
<li><p>Training</p></li>
<li><p>Run research proposal before Review Board</p>
<ul>
<li><p>Strover is RTF liaison</p></li>
<li><p>Write a research proposal</p>
<ul>
<li><p>Use form that they expect:</p>
<ul>
<li><p>Title and list of investigators</p></li>
<li><p>goals of the project (WHY - clear RQs)</p></li>
<li><p>background/significance (references a plus - show you’re familiar with research)</p></li>
<li><p>Research Method/Design</p>
<ul>
<li><p>Describe what you’re doing</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li><p>Human Subjects Interaction</p>
<ul>
<li><p>Who you’re using?</p></li>
<li><p>Nature of interactions?</p></li>
<li><p>recruitment process?</p></li>
<li><p>payment?</p></li>
<li><p>obtain consent (they have templates)?</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li><p>Research protocol (attached with other “instruments&quot;</p></li>
<li><p>Privacy and confidentiality (personal info, etc.)</p></li>
<li><p>Procedures for protecting data (personally identifiable information)</p></li>
<li><p>Risks</p></li>
<li><p>Resources</p></li>
<li><p>Benefits</p></li>
<li><p>Agencies involved</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
</section><section class="slide level2">
<h1>What about social media?</h1>
<ul>
<li><p>They want to know the specifics:</p>
<ul>
<li><p>Sites?</p></li>
<li><p>Types of interactions?</p></li>
<li><p>Personally identifiable information?</p></li>
<li><p>Identity yourself and what you’re doing. For informed consent.</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li><p>Be open, honest and transparent with IRB about what you’re doing.</p></li>
<li><p>How do you get informed consent in *~CyBeRsPaCe~*?</p>
<ul>
<li><p>Survey - informed consent page?</p>
<ul>
<li><p>Affirmative choice to take survey</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li><p>For a group?</p>
<ul>
<li><p>How did you get in? What is your role/subjects role?</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
